programme.title: Telemovie: Mak-Mak Kesayangan
programme.desc: Salina seorang sukarelawan Pusat Jagaan Nurul Jannah iaitu pusat jagaan warga emas perempuan. Salina menjadi sukarelawan kerana menyesal dengan perbuatannya mengabaikan ibunya dulu. Salina memanggil mereka dengan panggilan Mak, Umi dan Bonda. Faris turut menghantar ibunya di situ. Ibu Faris, Mak Minah mempunyai penyakit Alzheimer. Mak Minah hilang ketika berada di pusat jagaan kerana mencari Faris. Faris telah meletakkan ibunya terus di pusat jagaan itu sehingga ibunya meninggal dunia. Salina berkahwin dengan Faris. Setelah berkahwin, Faris tidak membenarkan Salina ke pusat itu. Mak mak semua rindu dengan Salina.

Mereka perlu beraksi dengan menggerakkan bibir mereka tanpa suara (lip sync) seperti mereka sedang menyanyi mengikut lirik lagu yang dipilih oleh mereka. Kali ini juga, dua mini game perlu dilakukan mereka iaitu meneka bibir penyanyi dan tiupan tisu. Di akhir perang bibir kali ini, Mawar Rashid muncul juara mengumpul 203 markah mengalah Izzue Islam yang mengumpul 160 markah dan Taufiq Hanafi 122 markah. programme.title: Pinggan Tak Retak Nasi Tak Dingin Ep08
programme.desc: Memaparkan Hani menemani Sheila yang sakit hendak bersalin. Sheila memarahi dan meminta Hani tidak perlu menemainya. Hani sabar, tenang sebaliknya memaklumkan dia berbuat demikian atas kehendak ibu dan bapa mertua mereka. Setelah Hani menasihatinya dan meminta Sheila banyak istigfar dan berdoa daripada mengeluh dan ingat yang bukan-bukan, Sheila akhirnya berubah positif terhadap Hani. Nizam yang dihubungi Hani tidak menjawab. Sheila selamat melahirkan anaknya dan dia kekurangan darah dan Hani telah mendermanya. Mizan pula dimaklumkan Khalid tentang wanita idamannya tidak kelihatan beberapa hari. Jadi rancangan untuk menemuinya ditangguhkan dahulu. Sebelum itu Khalid juga bertanyakan Yusri tentang Hani tetapi Yusri juga tidak ketahui. Hani yang menjagai adik iparnya juga membantu ibu mentuanya di rumah. Dia keletihan dan ibunya meminta dia berehat dan tidur awal. Mizan pula mengutamakan ke kampungnya daripada majlis jemputan tetapi tiba lewat malam, Hani telah nyenyak tidur. Sheila berkali-kali menghantar pesanan ringkas kepada Nizam tetapi tiada sebarang jawapan. Dia juga teringat kisah lalu bagaimana bekas rakan lelakinya yang tidak mahu bertanggungjawab dan kemudiannya bertemu dengan Nizam.

Fara pula mula raih perhatian Zafuan yang agak ‘slow’ dalam memikat perempuan. Juliana cuba ganggu pertemuan Haryati dan Suzan. Tapi Haryati pula nasihatinya agar terima kenyataan andainya jodoh Aidid dengan Suzan. Suatu hari, Aidid ajak Haryati teman dia dan Suzan pergi majlis kenduri di rumah keluarga Sy Kamarudian. Tapi di sana, Haryati terkejut bila dia mengenali ibu dan ayah Sy Kamarudin itu.

programme.title: Cintaku Di Bumi Izmir Ep11
programme.desc: Aidid kecewa sebab Suzan langsung tak jawab panggilannya. Mujurlah Fara selalu maklumkan hal Suzan padanya. Suzan jadi pendiam dan tertekan sampai jatuh sakit. Mrs Lale mula simpati padanya. Aidid akhirnya bantah kehendak Haryati dan terbang ke Izmir senyap-senyap. Di Izmir, Suzan masih enggan terima dan maafkan dia walaupun Fara sama-sama bantu cari jalan nak pujuk Suzan. Akhirnya, Aidid ambil tindakan berani ketemu dengan Mrs Lale dan akui cintanya pada Suzan. Depan Mrs Lale sendiri Aidid lamar Suzan jadi isterinya dan minta Mrs Lale buat keputusan tentangnya.

programme.title: Cintaku Di Bumi Izmir Ep12
programme.desc: Mrs Lale setuju Aidid dan Suzan nikah. Mereka mula buat persiapan kawin ikut adat Turki. Namun Suzan masih tak yakin. Tapi akhirnya, Aidid berjaya yakinkan Suzan yang dia ikhlas nak bahagiakan Suzan. Lepas nikah, mereka bulan madu di Alacati. Ketika ini Suzan tahu yang Aidid ada masalah tidur gara-gara trauma selepas kematian orang tua. Suzan cuba bantu Aidid tangani masalah itu. Aidid setuju biar Suzan tinggal di Izmir hingga hari konvo. Tapi dia pula dapat mesej dari Haryati yang teruskan majlis tunangnya dengan Juliana. Maka Aidid terpaksa bawa Suzan balik.

Syifa beritahu mamanya bangun awal dan kurang tidur kerana banyak dapat tempahan menjual cookies dan kek batik secara online. Rahim kemudian tempah kek dari mama mereka melalui Syifa. Mahani jugak pelik suaminya nampak berubah sejak kehadiran Syifa dan Haikal. Rahim terharu setelah merasa kek Maya, dia teringatkan Maya pernah buat kek batik semasa hari ulangtahunnya dan Mahani dahulu. Maya terkejut terima jumlah bayaran kek yang begitu banyak. Syifa cuba mengelak untuk menjawab, begitu juga Hisyam. Mereka juga terpaksa berdalih tentang baju-baju baru yang mahal, kononnya papa belikan separuh harga. Sebenarnya Hani amat menyayangi ibu mentuanya yang mengharapkan Hanilah yang dapat memujuk Nizam. Sebenarnya perbualan Hani dan Nizam semata-mata mengharap Nizam balik berjumpa ibu dan Sheila. malahan dalam perbualan dia meminta Nizam lupakan sahaja kisah mereka. Dia juga bertegas ketaatsetianya hanyalah kepada suaminya. Berikutan itu Nizam anggapkan Hani tidak lagi sukakannya. Dalam pada itu Mizan yang tidak tahu sepenuhnya bualan Hani terus andaikan isterinya masih sukakan Nizam. Mizan berubah tingkah laku dan kemudiannya disedari Hani punca daripadanya. Hani cuba meminta maaf dan ingin menjelaskan kedudukan sebenar. Mizan masih marah dan cemburu tanpa usul periksa. Kebetulan Mizan terlihat lukisan-lukisan Hani, dari lukisan jelas yang Hani benar-benar cinta dan sukakannya. Mizan dan Hani saling maaf bermaafan selepas itu dan Mizan langsung tidak mencurigai, malahan hubungan mereka kini lebih mesra. Mizan juga amat ceria ke pejabat hingga menghairankan rakan sekerja. Suraya di Langkawi kebetulan bertemu Nizam. Nizam tahu Suraya masih mahukan abangnya, justeru dengan gambar-gambar aktiviti sosial Suraya yang ada, Nizam seolah-olah mengugut Suraya. Nizam mahukan Suraya dapat berperanan untuk mengeruhkan perhubungan Mizan dengan isterinya sehingga mereka bercerai.

programme.title: Mantera Anjasmoro Ep7
programme.desc: Episod ini mengisahkan keadaan Suria semakin teruk dan bertindak ganas seperti dirasuk hantu. Zahid juga jarang datang menengok Suria. Bomoh wanita yang membuat santau untuk Suria juga mati dalam keadaan ngeri. Bapa meminta bantuan Ustaz Ibrahim, dalam perjalanan untuk membantu Suria, uztas pula terkorban dalam kemalangan jalanraya. Seterusnya, Suria pula mati di hospital dalam keadaan ngeri.

programme.title: Gonjiam: Haunted Asylum
programme.desc: Krew siri web seram pergi ke rumah puaka terbiar untuk siaran langsung. Mereka akan menemui sesuatu lebih daripada yang dijangkakan apabila mereka bergerak lebih dalam ke dalam bangunan lama yang mengerikan itu.

programme.title: Mantera Anjasmoro Ep8
programme.desc: Episod ini mengisahkan selepas kematian Suria, Zahid dan keluarga sering diganggu bayang dan suara Suria. Gangguan itu menyebabkan kandungan Sabrina gugur. Zahid menemui barang barang pelik di bilik Suria yang menunjukkan selama ini Suria mengamalkan ilmu santau. Lalu, Zahid berbaik semula dengan Sabrina. Sementara iru, Sabrina masih meneruskan perjumpaan dengan Ramona yang memberikan dia ilmu untuk melindungi diri dari hantu Suria dan juga menguasai orang lain. Seterusnya, di tempat kerja, Sabrina berkenalan dengan Irfan yang jatuh hati dengan Sabrina.

programme.title: Beyond Skyline
programme.desc: Seorang detektif memulakan usaha tanpa henti untuk membebaskan anaknya daripada kapal perang asing yang ngeri.

programme.title: Muzium Misteri Ep6
programme.desc: Mengisahkan encik Bad kini sedar kekasinya telah menipunya, kononnya wang RM 5,000 yang diberi pinjam untuk kos rawatan, sebaliknya kekasihnya telah menghilangkan diri. Anak dan isteri yang dicerainya telah menyindir-nyindirnya. Sementara itu Adam, Shah dan Daniel terus berusaha mencari lembaga lilin yang diharapkan encik Bad. Sementara itu Nur juga berselfie dengan Shah dan di tengah gambar mereka wujud lembaga lilin, menjadi kerisauan Nur. Nur mengadu kepada ibunya dan di samping itu Nur juga bertindak menjadi perantaraan agar ibu dan bapanya berbaik semula. Shah, Adam dan Daniel telah berbincang dengan profesor dan mendapat nasihat lanjut tentang sukarnya lembaga lilin untuk ditangkap. Di samping itu, Shah dan Adam masih berusaha memikat Nur walaupun Nur membayangkan dia menyukai Shah. Adam juga mengesyaki Shah memikat Nur tetapi masih berpura-pura. Usaha yang berterusan dengan bantuan rakan wanita Daniel, akhirnya lembaga lilin muncul dan dengan mensasarkan lilin hingga padam, akhirnya lembaga lilin berjaya ditangkap dan mengembirakan encik Bad kerana muzuimnya di kunjungi ramai

programme.title: Khun Pan 2
programme.desc: Di tengah-tengah pelanggaran undang-undang dan rasuah, detektif polis legenda Khun Pan menyertai kumpulan penyamun yang menggerunkan tetapi bergelut dengan kesetiaannya.

programme.title: Dendam Sarakit S1 Ep2
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Sarakit dirogol empat lelaki bertopeng sementara seorang lagi, Ramdi, diminta menjaga di luar rumah. Keesokan hari, ibu bapa Sarakit pergi menjenguk Sarakit dan mendapati rumahnya berkunci dan tiada respon dari Sarakit. Mereka terserempak dengan Pak Bado yang mengadu bahawa Sarakit sudah sombong setelah berkahwin dengan Rafiq dan melanggar adat resam kampung. Sarakit yang sangat lemah dan tidak berdaya untuk bangun dan bersuara mendengar perbualan mereka. Sementara itu, Mariam masih enggan membenarkan Rafiq pulang ke Sarakit atas alasan dia sakit dan cuba mendekatkan Rafiq dengan Dina, bekas teman wanitanya. Pada masa yang sama, Ramdi sering diganggu oleh lembaga putih berambut panjang yang setiap malam merayau-rayau di kampung sambil menangis dan memohon maaf. Pada satu malam, Kiol, salah seorang yang merogol Sarakit, dicekik lembaga putih berambut panjang dan mayatnya dijumpai di sungai dengan jari kelingkingnya dipotong.

programme.title: The Presence
programme.desc: Aom dihantui mimpi ngeri yang tidak dapat dijelaskan. Semasa melawat neneknya, dia mendapat tahu bahawa neneknya yang kelihatan lebih mati daripada hidup sedang melayan dan memberi makan kepada hantu. Adakah Aom akan menerima nasibnya?

programme.title: Arwah Tumbal Nyai the Trilogy Part Arwah
programme.desc: Syurkiani sangat ingin tahu mengapa dia selalu dilarang oleh neneknya, Lela untuk belajar tarian jaipong. Diam-diam Syurkiani datang kepada Nyi Imas, bekas penari jaipong untuk belajar tarian. Nyi Imas meminta Syurkiani memukul gendang misteri tiga kali sebagai syarat. Bagaimanapun, Syurkiani memukul gendang sebanyak empat kali. Selepas kejadian itu nenek Syurkiani meninggal dunia kerana diserang oleh makhluk ghaib. Syurkiani juga menjadi sasaran makhluk ghaib kerana memanggil roh dengan memukul gendang sebanyak empat kali. Syukriani dan teman lelakinya, Shakti, cuba melarikan diri dari serangan itu.

programme.title: Gonjiam: Haunted Asylum
programme.desc: Aom dihantui mimpi ngeri yang tidak dapat dijelaskan. Semasa melawat neneknya, dia mendapat tahu bahawa neneknya yang kelihatan lebih mati daripada hidup sedang melayan dan memberi makan kepada hantu. Adakah Aom akan menerima nasibnya?

programme.title: You Saka..Pergi Jauh-jauh S1 Ep1
programme.desc: Episod Pertama cereka komedi seram disusuli dengan kepercayaan khurafat ini berkisar kepada personaliti Nia. Nia sebagai setiausaha syarikat milik seorang Datin Salina yang amat menyukainya hingga bercadang untuk dijodohkan kepada anak lelakinya. Ibu Nia dikampung, sedang sakit dijagai oleh Roslan, bapa saudaranya (Pak Lang). Nia mempercayai dia wajar menyeru puteri yang sesekali Nia akan lakukan bertujuan melindunginya dan juga sebagai amalan turun temurunnya selama ini. Jika tidak dilakukan, saka berbentuk syaitan akan menggangguinya. Ada sebab-sebab bahawa ibunya memiliki saka dan kematiannya bererti saka itu cuba mempengaruhi warisnya iaitu Nia. Nia tinggal dengan Shasa dan sepupu Shasa iaitu, Adrus adalah 'boy friend' Nia. Adrus sedang menceburi kerjaya dalam bidang paranormal, merupakan anak Ibrahim seorang bomoh. Ketika ibu Nia meninggal dunia dia belum ketahui. Sementara itu, semasa pengembumian ibunya berlaku juga kekecuhan iaitu muncul lembaga putih (berbentuk manusia - wanita). Selain dari itu, sesekali saka Gelam berbentuk syaitan (hitam jalur hijau) mengganggui Nia, 'boy friend'nya dan pernah bersama lembaga putih mengganggui bomoh Ibrahim.

programme.title: Santau Merasuk Ep2
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Hawa (ibu Halim) yang datang dari kampung, menasihati Hawa dan Nina supaya menerima takdir. Halim merasakan dia boleh mengendalikan pemasalahannya sama Nina itu dengan caranya. Hawa yang menyedari anaknya itu diganggu sesuatu menasihatkani Hawa supaya berubat tetapi tidak diendahkan. Halim merasa bosan dengan ibunya dan menghantar pulang ke kampung

programme.title: 3AM Ep2
programme.desc: Seorang gadis sekolah menyertai dua pencipta kandungan internet dalam projek video seram yang dirakamkan di bangunan lama di belakang sekolah mereka. Ketiga-tiga mereka bertemu dengan kumpulan pembuli dan apabila peristiwa berlaku, menjadi jelas bahawa gadis itu menyimpan dendam peribadi terhadap kumpulan itu dan dibutakan oleh kebencian untuk melaksanakan keadilan, walaupun ia bermakna mengorbankan orang yang tidak bersalah…

programme.title: Seekers Underground Ep910
programme.desc: Seekers kembali dengan nama baru Seekers Underground. Dengan teknologi baru serta tinjaun ke lokasi yang belum pernah diterokai

programme.title: Bodyguard S1 Ep10
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Nasha melarikan diri kerana tidak dapat menerima kenyataan Dato' Amir dan Mak Jah adalah ibu bapa kandungnya. Farish akhirnya berjumpa Nasha, dia memujuknya menerima kenyataan sebenar. Nasha kemudiannya menerima hakikat tersebut. Farish juga berjaya memujuk ibu dan bapanya menerima Nasha sebagai menantu mereka. Danial masih menjadi bodyguard Eliza, dia berjanji akan menjaga Eliza seperti diamanahkan. Rashid telah diberitahu oleh ibunya, dia dan Eliza sebenarnya adalah adik-beradik. Rashid kemudiannya dimanahkan untuk menguruskan syarikat Dato' Zaidi. Rahul pula sebagai bodyguard Maya berjaya mengesan Boboy yang telah menghilangkan diri. Maya berjanji akan menjadi ibu yang terbaik, dia bersama-sama dengan Mikhail dan Zulaikha akan memberipenjagaan kepada Boboy.

programme.title: Juara
programme.desc: Bisma, seorang remaja yang mempunyai bakat seni mempertahankan diri semula jadi menyukai Bella, seorang gadis di kolejnya. Tetapi teman lelakinya, Attar sentiasa mengganggu Bisma sehingga seorang lelaki misteri melatihnya untuk melawan.

programme.title: Dendam Sarakit S1 Ep3
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Mariam berjumpa Tok Moh yang mengatakan dia telah diganggu penjelmaan seorang wanita dan tidak lagi mahu berterusan dengan tugasan memisahkan Rafiq dan Sarakit. Mengimbas balik, Mariam enggan memberikan kebenaran untuk Rafiq berkahwin dengan Sarakit. Mariam telah berjumpa Tok Moh untuk memisahkan Rafiq dari Sarakit yang menyebabkan Sarakit diganggu mimpi ngeri. Kini, Mariam pula diganggu penjelmaan Sarakit dan perkara ini diceritakan kepada Rafiq. Rafiq mengambil keputusan untuk pulang kerana memikirkan Sarakit yang masih belum dapat dihubungi. Ramdi pula diganggu hantu tenggek yang dibawa merayau-rayau setiap malam. Pada satu malam, Pak Bado pula mendengar suara bayi menangis dan mendapati bungkusan mengandungi janin di hadapan rumahnya yang diletak oleh lembaga putih berambut panjang.

programme.title: Juara
programme.desc: Bisma, seorang remaja yang mempunyai bakat seni mempertahankan diri semula jadi menyukai Bella, seorang gadis di kolejnya. Tetapi teman lelakinya, Attar sentiasa mengganggu Bisma sehingga seorang lelaki misteri melatihnya untuk melawan.

programme.title: Dendam Sarakit S1 Ep2
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Sarakit dirogol empat lelaki bertopeng sementara seorang lagi, Ramdi, diminta menjaga di luar rumah. Keesokan hari, ibu bapa Sarakit pergi menjenguk Sarakit dan mendapati rumahnya berkunci dan tiada respon dari Sarakit. Mereka terserempak dengan Pak Bado yang mengadu bahawa Sarakit sudah sombong setelah berkahwin dengan Rafiq dan melanggar adat resam kampung. Sarakit yang sangat lemah dan tidak berdaya untuk bangun dan bersuara mendengar perbualan mereka. Sementara itu, Mariam masih enggan membenarkan Rafiq pulang ke Sarakit atas alasan dia sakit dan cuba mendekatkan Rafiq dengan Dina, bekas teman wanitanya. Pada masa yang sama, Ramdi sering diganggu oleh lembaga putih berambut panjang yang setiap malam merayau-rayau di kampung sambil menangis dan memohon maaf. Pada satu malam, Kiol, salah seorang yang merogol Sarakit, dicekik lembaga putih berambut panjang dan mayatnya dijumpai di sungai dengan jari kelingkingnya dipotong.

programme.title: Khun Pan 2
programme.desc: Di tengah-tengah pelanggaran undang-undang dan rasuah, detektif polis legenda Khun Pan menyertai kumpulan penyamun yang menggerunkan tetapi bergelut dengan kesetiaannya.

programme.desc: Seekers kembali dengan nama baru Seekers Underground. Dengan teknologi baru serta tinjaun ke lokasi yang belum pernah diterokai

programme.title: Mumun
programme.desc: Mumun dan Juned adalah pasangan yang saling menyayangi. Walau bagaimanapun, Mumun meninggal dunia dalam satu kemalangan dan Juned sangat kecewa dengannya.

programme.title: Amukan Pocong S1 Ep4
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Awang berpuas hati kerana 2 mangsa sudah berjaya dikorbankan. Long Hussain yang masih segar dan bertenaga berjaya dipergunakan Awang dengan baik. Bila Awang mengesan mangsanya, roh Awang akan bersatu dengan jasad Long Hussain. Kali ini mangsanya adalah Mira, seorang usahawan andaman dan butik perkahwinan yang bekerja sendiri di rumah. Mira tinggal dengan kedua orang tuanya sementara adik beradiknya yang lain di Kuala Lumpur. Ketika orang tua Mira ke Kuala Lumpur Mira tinggal bersendirian. Mira diserang dan dibunuh oleh pocong.

programme.title: The Lake
programme.desc: Seorang kanak-kanak membawa balik telur aneh, sehingga menyedari bahawa ia adalah telur raksasa. Ia muncul dari tasik dan membunuh semua orang di seluruh bandar.

programme.title: Seekers Underground Ep910
programme.desc: Seekers kembali dengan nama baru Seekers Underground. Dengan teknologi baru serta tinjaun ke lokasi yang belum pernah diterokai

programme.title: Santau Merasuk Ep2
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Hawa (ibu Halim) yang datang dari kampung, menasihati Hawa dan Nina supaya menerima takdir. Halim merasakan dia boleh mengendalikan pemasalahannya sama Nina itu dengan caranya. Hawa yang menyedari anaknya itu diganggu sesuatu menasihatkani Hawa supaya berubat tetapi tidak diendahkan. Halim merasa bosan dengan ibunya dan menghantar pulang ke kampung

programme.title: Juara
programme.desc: Bisma, seorang remaja yang mempunyai bakat seni mempertahankan diri semula jadi menyukai Bella, seorang gadis di kolejnya. Tetapi teman lelakinya, Attar sentiasa mengganggu Bisma sehingga seorang lelaki misteri melatihnya untuk melawan.

programme.title: You Saka..Pergi Jauh-jauh S1 Ep2
programme.desc: Episod ke 2 mengisahkan ketika Nia berada di rumah bomoh Ibrahim dia sugul kerana sebelah malamnya dia diganggui oleh saka Gelam. Kemudiannya dia mendapat panggilan memaklumkan ibunya telah meninggal dunia. Dia pulang bersama Adrus dan seterusnya membincangkan dengan Pak Lang dan Pak Abas tentang kematian dan rancangan membuat tahlil. Kemudiannya majikannya mengetahui berita kematian itu dan memutuskan akan biaya kenduri arwah. Semasa kenduri arwah lembaga putih muncul, menyebabkan jadi gempar, tetapi Datin Salina yang berada di tepi lembaga itu tidak nampak apa-apa. Sewaktu Datin balik difahamkan lembaga putih mengekorinya. Di rumah Datin, lembaga putih hanya mengganggui anaknya Fauzan. Di siang hari Fauzan terasa seorang anak gadis cantik dikenali sebagai Rosserita melayaninya dengan berbual-bual di pengkarangan rumah. Ini membuatkan Datin mula kehairanan terhadap anaknya yang berubah perangai. Ini termasuk bersikap negatif semasa makan walau pun sebagai kali pertama menemui dan bersama Nia.

programme.title: Gonjiam: Haunted Asylum
programme.desc: Aom dihantui mimpi ngeri yang tidak dapat dijelaskan. Semasa melawat neneknya, dia mendapat tahu bahawa neneknya yang kelihatan lebih mati daripada hidup sedang melayan dan memberi makan kepada hantu. Adakah Aom akan menerima nasibnya?

programme.title: Mantera Anjasmoro Ep11
programme.desc: Episod ini mengisahkan Ibu Sabrina datang ke rumah kerana dia bimbang dan berasa sesuata yang tidak kenal pada Sabrina. Sebaik sahaja, ibu tiba di rumah Sabrina, ibu diganggu oleh pelbagai bunyi dan bayang, sehingga dia tidak tahan lagi dan pulang ke kampung. Seterusnya Zahid meluahkan perasaan yang dia teringin mengambil anak angkat. Sabrina marah dan memohon lagi bantuan Ramona untuk mengunci nafsu dan hati Zahid. Mantera yang dilakukan Ramona menyebabkan Zahid menghadapi kesakitan

programme.title: Amukan Pocong S1 Ep3
programme.desc: Mengisahkan ketika orang kampung masih lagi diselubungi misteri dengan kematian Zai, pocong muncul untuk mencari mangsa seterusnya. Sal yang bekerja sebagai pembantu kedai di pekan pulang agak lewat sedikit malam itu. Sal telah terserempak dengan pocong tersebut. Ini menyebabkan motor Sal terbabas dan pada masa itulah, Sal diserang pocong yang menyedut darahnya. Mayat Sal ditemui di atas pokok oleh ayah dan tunangnya. Esoknya sekali lagi kampung Paya Besar kecoh dengan kematian seorang lagi anak gadis.

programme.title: Hantu Bungkus VS Pontianak
programme.desc: Hantu Bungkus VS Pontianak

programme.title: Jengka
programme.desc: Nini mengalami keguguran semasa melarikan diri di ladang kelapa sawit. Namun, satu perkara aneh terjadi apabila bayinya dikatakan masih hidup dan dilarikan oleh penunggu. Orang kampung berusaha membantu mencari Nini dan anaknya, namun perkara seram terjadi sepanjang pencarian mereka.

programme.title: Azura 2012
programme.desc: Azura, seorang gadis remaja yang gigih hadapi cabaran hidup untuk mencapai cita-citanya. Dia tinggal bersama ibu saudaranya setelah kedua ibu bapanya meninggal dunia dalam satu tragedi. Azura kemudiannya menjadi mahasiswa di sebuah universiti swasta dan menjalinkan hubungan mesra dengan Zek, seorang anak hartawan. Walau bagaimanapun, cinta mereka dihalang oleh bapa Zek dan mereka terpaksa melalui pelbagai dugaan.

programme.title: Baginda
programme.desc: Diwariskan untuk mengurus sebuah kolej swasta di Johor Bahru oleh pakciknya, Azian terpaksa melalui pelbagai cabaran untuk menaikkan semula martabat sekolah yang sudah merudum prestasinya itu. Hampir sahaja putus asa namun sikap dedikasinya untuk mendidik anak bangsa membuatkan Azian ingin terus menjalankan amanah pakciknya.

programme.title: Scoop
programme.desc: Tania, seorang wartawan menjalankan penyiasatan tentang kes pembunuhan rakannya, Johari yang menyiasat skandal syarikat kewangan. Skandal tersebut melibatkan bapa Sheila. Dibantu oleh seorang jurufoto, Norman yang ingin membersihkan namanya kerana sebelum Johari mati dibunuh, terdapat pertengkaran antara mereka berdua. Mereka pun mula menyiasat punca sebenar pembunuhan Johari.

programme.title: Bukan Cinta Malaikat
programme.desc: Reyhan, seorang sukarelawan Muslim Care yang berasal dari Bandung jatuh hati kepada gadis Malaysia bernama Dewi sejak dia menyelamatkan Dewi daripada satu insiden ketika mereka berada di Madinah. Walau bagaimanapun, cinta Reyhan itu terhalang apabila Dewi mempunyai kekasih bernama Adam. Dalam masa yang sama, seorang gadis bernama Aliyah pula menaruh hati kepada Reyhan.

programme.title: XX Ray
programme.desc: Obsesinya terhadap angkasa lepas telah membuatkan Amir untuk mencipta sebuah topi keledar. Topi keledar ini merupakan penemuan baru apabila ia menggunakan kuasa tahi bintang. Sesiapa sahaja yang memakainya boleh melihat menembusi apa sahaja yang mereka inginkan. Kekacauan berlaku apabila topi itu telah menyebabkan Amir bertukar menjadi halimunan.

programme.title: XX Ray 2
programme.desc: Bekerja sebagai saintis kadet, Tina berasa ditipu apabila Johan mendakwa dia yang mencipta mesin pelupusan laser walhal ia merupakan hasil cetusan idea dari Tina. Ingin menghalang niat jahat Johan, Tina meminta bantuan Amir. Namun, keduanya terkena pancaran laser mesin itu dalam cubaan untuk menghalang Johan dan telah dihantar ke zaman Kesultanan Melayu Melaka.

programme.title: Gila - Gila Pengantin
programme.desc: Aliah seorang gadis yang ingin berkahwin tetapi mempunyai satu fobia dimana dia takut untuk bersanding dia atas pelamin setelah apa yang terjadi keatas dirinya semasa dia kecil. Dalam masa yang sama, Johari juga mempunyai masalah yang sama dengan Aliah. Mereka telah bertemu di dalam dunia cyber dan beramah mesra dengan perbualan masing-masing sehingga hari ini. Rupa-rupanya ada kenangan di antara mereka berdua. Namun mereka bakal berkahwin dengan pasangan yang berlainan dari mereka dan kedua-duanya perlu bersanding di atas pelamin ketika majlis perkahwinan.

programme.title: Gila - Gila Pengantin Remaja
programme.desc: Pasangan remaja yang bakal menduduki peperiksaan SPM, Amir dan Mastura berikrar ingin berkahwin selepas tamatnya pengajian di universiti. Namun, Fandi yang juga rakan sekelas Mastura mencemburui percintaan mereka. SPM pun tiba tetapi Mastura terlewat menghadiri ujian Matematik dan berasa amat kecewa kerana menganggap dia telah pun gagal. Kakak Mastura, Anita pula ingin Mastura mencari calon suami yang kaya. Perasaan kecewa mula menyelubungi diri Amir apabila mendapat tahu Mastura ditunangkan dengan Fandi. Mengetahui perihal sebenar mengapa mereka akan dikahwinkan, Amir membawa Mastura lari ke selatan Thailand. Bermulalah kekecohan antara mereka semua dalam sekuel kepada Gila-Gila Pengantin ini.

programme.title: Puteri Impian
programme.desc: Pekerja kilang, Puteri Nora sentiasa mengimpikan untuk menjadi seorang puteri raja. Impiannya menjadi kenyataan apabila dia diterima menyertai pertandingan "Memburu Impian". Kehidupannya berubah sekelip mata apabila bertemu Tengku Faizal, seorang putera raja. Namun, Zul, jurukameranya dalam rancangan itu turut menyukai Puteri Nora. Pilihan harus dibuat antara kemewahan atau kebebasan.

programme.title: Puteri Impian 2
programme.desc: Gadis kilang yang menolak lamaran seorang kerabat diraja Tengku Faizal, menaruh hati terhadap jurukamera stesen televisyen, Zul. Nora menyukai Zul tetapi dia telah pun menjalin hubungan bersama Lisa. Adik kepada Tengku Faizal, Tengku Farid ingin membawa semula Nora kembali ke abangnya. Tekad, dia ingin mengangkat semula maruah abangnya.

programme.title: Femina
programme.desc: Perjuangan untuk mendapatkan hak setara antara jantina terutamanya wanita lantang dibicarakan di dalam majalah Femina. Tina, tegas memperjuangkan pendiriannya manakala Anita tidak berapa menyukai cara Tina. Femina telah menjadi satu platform anti-lelaki. Pertemuan Tina bersama Pyan mula mengubah pandangan ekstrem Tina namun perasaan dilema mula menguasai diri apabila dituduh sebagai pembelot wanita.

programme.title: 2022 Tsunami
programme.desc: Pada tahun 2022, Perdana Menteri Tribhop dan Dr. Siam menubuhkan pusat amaran bencana negara untuk mengelakkan bencana tsunami yang lain. Tetapi usaha mereka terbukti sia-sia apabila tragedi melanda lagi.

programme.title: It Takes A Man And Women
programme.desc: Jalan cerita tentang seorang gadis miskin yang bekerja dengan seorang lelaki kaya di sebuah syarikat penerbitan majalah. Dia bercinta dengan lelaki tersebut namun lelaki itu telah berlaku curang kerana mementingkan diri. Gadis tersebut pergi membawa diri ke Amerika Syarikat untuk bekerja dan setelah beberapa tahun dia menjadi seorang perunding penerbitan yang berjaya dan professional. Suatu hari, syarikat lelaki tersebut mengalami masalah dan memerlukan seorang perunding penerbitan. Lembaga pengarah telah menghantar gadis itu untuk menjadi perunding bagi menyelamatkan syarikat tersebut.

programme.desc: Seorang gangster veteran, Dollah yang selalu bermimpi menjadi pelakon mendapat peluang seumur hidup apabila pelakon popular memintanya untuk menjadi mentornya untuk filem aksi. Seorang samseng di lokasi penggambaran, Dollah pasti menimbulkan pelbagai kekacauan.

programme.title: Pening-Pening Lalat
programme.desc: Dino adalah banduan yang berjaya melarikan diri dari penjara. Polis menyiarkan berita mengenainya dan menawarkan hadiah RM10,000 kepada sesiapa yang berjaya menangkapnya. Jadi Dino bersembunyi di dalam hutan di mana dia bertemu Zakaria dan Aliza.

programme.desc: Seorang eksekutif muda, istrinya, dan putrinya mengalami keanehan hantu di rumah mereka.

programme.desc: <Stylish Man – The Chef> is co-hosted by the Golden Bell Awards winner Sam Tseng, Bernice Tsai and Genie Chuo, together with two professional chefs, A-Chi and James. There are two main themes for the program, which are “Big Stars Come to Cook” and “Five-Star Cooking Show”. <Stylish Man – The Chef> containing not only the bomb of laughter, but the audience can also gain practical cooking knowledge throughout the program.

programme.title: The Tradition Story of Taiwan (T) Ep46134614
programme.desc: The Tradition Story of Taiwan presents a series of tales and folktales in Taiwan that have been pass down from one generation to another generation

programme.title: Taste of Life (T) Ep10731074
programme.desc: Chu-Tsai,Chao and his wife Chin-hsiu,Li have five children. Devoted all his life into developing soy sauce products, Chu-Tsai very much hopes that one of his kids can follow his footsteps and take over his business, but he also respects their own passions and aspirations. Because of their father’s invention dream, the Chao brothers’ lives are about to change… Chin-Pang,Chou used to be Chin-Hsiu’s lover, and has been Chu-Tsai’s long-time business rival. Seeing Chu-Tsai not only successfully keep the patents of soy sauce products, but also has all the support and assistance from his children, Chin-Pang, filled with bitterness, has been crushing and attacking Chu-Tsai in every way. Hsin-Ta, Chu-Tsai’s eldest son, couldn’t bear to see his father suffer, so he quit his job to take over the family business. To everyone’s surprise, Chu-Tsai discovers that Hsin-Ta is actually Chin-Pang’s son! Finding out that the enemy is actually his biological father devastated Hsin-Ta, and this also drives a wedge between Chin-pang and his son Hsiao-Ming, as he feels threatened. Chu-tsai’s second son Ying-kai has always set his goal to reach the top of his career. Vacillating between Mei-mei and Ying-hui, Ying-kai also finds himself caught in between the feud of two families; however, this opens new business opportunities for him. On the other hand, Hsin-ta fulfills Chu-tsai’s dream; but he is more confused than ever about family love and romance love… All he knows is that with the family’s support, his determination and conviction, he can build a future of his own!

programme.title: Hot Door Night (M) Ep1811
programme.desc: Different in age, generation, and hosting style, these three hosts not only can sing, act, dance, and imitate, but are also skilled in cross-talk! With this unique combination, we hope to attract viewers of all ages and spark great entertainment.

programme.title: iWalker-Monday (M)(repeat) Ep7
programme.desc: iWalker is a TV program which introduce food and attractive places to audience.

programme.title: Genghis Khan
programme.desc: Before he became the great Khan he was known as Temüjin, and was deeply in love with his childhood sweetheart Börte. News of Temüjin's father's death disrupted their relationship and as Temüjin heads back home, he faces a sudden attack from his father's former comrades, causing his whole tribe to be destroyed.

programme.title: Echoes of the Rainbow
programme.desc: Set in Hong Kong in the 1960s, the story revolves around the family of a hardworking shoemaker Mr Law, with his happy-go-lucky wife and two sons – a talented elder son and an eight-year-old eccentric younger son. While their lives are not always smooth-sailing, the family sticks together and support one another through thick and thin.

programme.title: The Way We Keep Dancing
programme.desc: This sequel of “The Way We Dance” features the plight of Hong Kong’s grassroots performing artists as they fight against the government’s plan to gentrify an industrial district where they settled in.

programme.title: The Calling of a Bus Driver
programme.desc: A girl named Suki fulfills her dream of being a bus driver after breaking up with her boyfriend, who has an affair with her good friend. When Suki is invited to attend her ex-boyfriend’s wedding, she is presented with a chance for revenge – will she take it and turn her life around?

programme.title: Legendary Amazons
programme.desc: Produced by Jackie Chan, this is the story about the fabled Yang family of female generals in feudal China. Yang Zong Bao, the last man standing in the Yang family, dies in a battle when defending the Song Dynasty from invaders. Zong Bao’s wife Mu Gui Ying steps up to lead other widows of the Yang’s into battle to continue their husband’s legacy.

programme.title: Secret Diary of a Mom To Be, The
programme.desc: A high-flying PR manager and her loving husband swear by a childless lifestyle but she is shocked to learn that she is expecting just when things look bright for a promotion! How would they deal with the unexpected surprises that life throws in their way?

programme.title: American Girl
programme.desc: 13 year-old Fen is uprooted from LA and moves to Taipei in early 2003, when her mother is diagnosed with breast cancer. She struggles to adjust to her new life with a new school and long-separated father, and drifts away from her mother. When her younger sister is misdiagnosed with SARS, they finally open up to each other during quarantine.

programme.title: Detective Chinatown 3
programme.desc: After the events in Bangkok and New York, Tang Ren and Qin Feng are invited to solve a murder case in Tokyo, but it turns out to be a challenge for the world’s best detectives. While the case has become complicated and confusing since the world’s top detective got involved, a hilarious challenge for the best detectives in Asia has just begun…

programme.title: New Kung Fu Cult Master 2
programme.desc: In this sequel, Zhang Wu Ji successfully rescued the Six Major sects at Dadu. Nevertheless, the quest for the Dragon Sabre continues as Wu Ji and his three girlfriends set sail for Ice Fire Island. After a series of vicious fights, they finally unveil the secret behind the Heaven Sword and Dragon Sabre.

programme.title: Dummy Mommy, without a Baby
programme.desc: Fong Lai Kuen works at an advertising agency but is about to be sacked by her boss after offending him. She pretends to be pregnant so that the company cannot fire her, according to the labour law. Since then, Fong receives much care and love from her colleagues and begins to feel guilty about her lie as things develop out of her expectations.

programme.title: I Fine… Thank You… Love You
programme.desc: Pleng, an English tutor, helps her student to pass a break up message in English to her boyfriend Gym. Gym knows nothing about English but wants to win back his girlfriend from the US, so he asks Pleng to teach him. Boorish and a slow learner, Gym makes many hilarious mistakes when learning English and ends up falling for Pleng.

programme.title: Defying Chase
programme.desc: A stunt man is inadvertently caught in a criminal operation involving culture relics hustling, and has to fight for himself in a series of dangerous adventures.

programme.title: Trivisa
programme.desc: In the beginning of 1997, Hong Kong's three notorious thieves who have never met one another before appear in the same restaurant. This leads to a rumour that they are joining forces to pull off something big before the Handover, though this is not something that any of them is aware of.

programme.title: The Macaque Monkey
programme.desc: The world is in chaos after the tree of life was burnt. Sun Wu Kong decides to return to the past to resurrect it, but his divine power is unstable after losing the golden hoop, and he must find his younger self to team up to find the power of time. As the six-eared Macaque Monkey also wants the power of time, they clash in a fierce battle…

programme.title: Knockout
programme.desc: A former boxing champion and convict who has just been released from prison discovers that his wife has died and he is now a single parent. The situation is made worse with his daughter’s diagnosis of leukaemia. In order to encourage his daughter and fulfil his promise of never giving up, he re-enters the boxing ring.

programme.title: My Kickass Wife
programme.desc: Jade is a beautiful royal guard who is set up for marriage by the Queen in order to avoid the King setting eyes on her. Jade falls for Sean and helps him win the contest for her. After the wedding, Sean discovers her bad temper and visits a brothel in his despair. He meets and is attracted to a girl there, not knowing she has a secret agenda...

programme.title: Rhapsody of Kidnapping
programme.desc: When three tech founders end up handing over their latest inventions to a sleazy tycoon who takes them for granted, they decide to kidnap the man’s wife, mistress, love child and his grandma for a huge ransom. Little did they expect that the heartless tycoon has hired an assassin to take them out instead of paying the ransom.

programme.title: A Cool Fish
programme.desc: In this dark-comedy, cop-turned-security guard Ma faces the ultimate challenge when his boss mysteriously disappears and his paralyzed sister makes a morbid deal with the armed bandits who abduct her.

programme.title: I Fine… Thank You… Love You
programme.desc: Pleng, an English tutor, helps her student to pass a break up message in English to her boyfriend Gym. Gym knows nothing about English but wants to win back his girlfriend from the US, so he asks Pleng to teach him. Boorish and a slow learner, Gym makes many hilarious mistakes when learning English and ends up falling for Pleng.

programme.title: Rise of the Legend
programme.desc: The young Wong Fei Hung is a fearless fighter who aligns himself with one of the two gang leaders ruling Guangzhou. However, there is more to the young Wong Fei Hung than meets the eye as he has a more dangerous agenda in mind.

programme.title: Find Your Voice
programme.desc: The “passion choir pilot program” trains students from three underperforming schools’ choir to participate in an inter-school choral competition. While it seems impossible, a renowned conductor, Yim Tsz Long, unexpectedly agrees to lead the choir. Will the “passion choir” and Maestro Yim complete this impossible mission and win the competition?

programme.title: The Bodyguard
programme.desc: A retired bodyguard who is suffering from early stages of dementia befriends a young girl whose life is threatened when her father falls in with the international crime world. The girl disappeared one day, and the bodyguard vows to save the life of his young friend.

programme.title: Two Tigers
programme.desc: This crime comedy is about a bumbling young man Fang Nan, who kidnaps a middle-aged businessman Zhang Cheng Gong for ransom. However, the captor becomes the captive when Zhang turns the tables on Fang and forces him to complete three tasks. The two men soon find themselves sharing a journey filled with absurdity and deception.

programme.title: Quan Dao: The Journey of a Boxer
programme.desc: Ah Niu learns boxing from Uncle Xing, the boss of a boxing studio, since young and uses his skills to help the weak fight villains. When Xing’s son attempts drug trafficking to save his father’s studio but fails and is brutally beaten up, Ah Niu accepts a death combat challenge so as to help him take revenge.

programme.title: Touch of the Light
programme.desc: A blind but talented pianist Siang encounters an unrecognized but skilful dancer Chieh. Chieh is attracted to the courageous Siang while Siang is fascinated by the adventurous Chieh. Their friendship grows as Siang and Chieh pursue their dreams together. Sandrine Pinna was awarded Best Actress for her role as Chieh in the 2012 Taipei Film Festival.

programme.title: The Singing Escort
programme.desc: Betty Ting plays Susan, a young woman hiding from her father by being a nightclub singer in Japan. Pop singer Chao Ke-jen (Lin Chong) gets permission from his boss to visit Japan, with the condition that he finds the boss's daughter. Boy finds girl, boy falls in love. But will the father approve?

programme.title: The Avenging Eagle
programme.desc: Chik, one of the assassins of the Iron Boat Clan, decides to leave the clan when a kind family saved him. When pursued by the clan, a swordsman whose wife was killed by him saved his life. They decide to jointly take revenge on the clan.

programme.title: The Brave Archer
programme.desc: On his way back to the midlands, Guo Jing meets Huang Rong and they quickly fall in love. However, Ouyang Ke proposes to marry Huang Rong at the same time, so Huang’s father sets up a duel for the two men to compete for her hand. Guo Jing finally beats Ouyang Ke to win Huang Rong back.

programme.title: The Voyage of Emperor Chien Lung
programme.desc: Emperor Chien Lung continues his incognito voyage to southern China. Accompanied by the minister and the imperial scholar, they have many amusing encounters in Yangzhou.

programme.title: Song Of Orchid Island
programme.desc: Dr. He moves to the remote Lanyu island off the coast of Taiwan to look for his long lost father, and starts to run a clinic curing islanders who are bitten by the fatal red worms there. He meets Ya Lan who works as a nurse in his clinic and falls in love with him. Things get vicious for Dr. He as a jealous islander plots to get rid of him…

programme.title: Pursuit of Vengeance
programme.desc: Kung Fu legend Ti Lung stars in the action movie as Fu Xue Hong, embarking on a epic journey of revenge for his father.

programme.title: We Love Millionaires
programme.desc: In this romantic comedy, three beautiful Hong Kong salesgirls travel to Osaka in Japan to pursue their dreams of marrying a rich man. They masquerade as high society debutantes and make their way to a posh resort to meet and woo millionaires (or fake ones!).

programme.title: Trilogy Of Swordsmanship
programme.desc: A kung fu anthology film consisting of three stories: a man embarrasses himself while trying to prove his worth to the father of the woman he loves; a courtesan in love with a general will need to deliver a notorious bandit in exchange for him not being executed; and a group of bandits forms a plan to rescue a new friend from being executed.

programme.title: The 5 Billion Dollar Legacy
programme.desc: A crippled billionaire mails a letter to each of his long-lost daughters inviting them to go to Japan, in the hope that he will find a worthy heir to inherit his vast fortune. The sisters finally meet abroad the plane to Japan, and one of them is taken with a man who is going to investigate the death of his lawyer uncle in a mysterious hit-and-run.

programme.title: The Sword Stained with Royal Blood
programme.desc: Adapted from the novel by Jin Yong, havoc breaks out when a warrior on the run uncovers a sword, training manual, treasure map & a secret message on the body of a deceased martial arts master.

programme.title: A Friend from Inner Space
programme.desc: A young boy whose parents are separated tries to find happiness in life. One day, he meets and befriends a kind-hearted spirit Ren, who decides to make him truly happy by getting his parents back together.

programme.title: The Golden Knight
programme.desc: The heroine Yu Fei Xia is accused of stealing the book of martial arts secrets. To prove her innocence, she disguises herself as a man and finds her way into the Shaolin Temple to find out the truth...

programme.title: The Delinquent
programme.desc: This is a coming-of-age tale depicting the lower class Hong Kong troubled youths in the 1960s and the societal issues that they face. Wang Chung is a hotheaded and rebellious teen who is tempted by the dark side, and have to unfortunately pay a huge price for it.

programme.title: A Deadly Secret
programme.desc: A corrupt magistrate, obsessed with finding a hidden treasure, jails and tortures his daughter's lover and buries his daughter alive! Ironically, it is in her coffin that the secret to the hidden treasure is found, setting off a frenzy of destruction.

programme.title: Whose Baby is in the Classroom?
programme.desc: Chen, a male teacher in an all girls’ high school, is stuck with a baby that isn’t his and must take care of it. As he lives on the school grounds, the baby is a source of constant distraction and worry! Luckily, his class warms to the baby and helps him take care of it while he works his charm on Li Ching, an uptight teacher in the same school.

programme.title: Brothers from the Walled City
programme.desc: Two orphaned brothers growing up in Kowloon's Walled City - the place where people are forced to live with indecent businesses of sex, gambling and drugs controlled by triads - take very different life paths. Chin works at a cabaret but keeps away from sins, while Kang is drawn to the sleazy underworld. Are their destinies shaped by the “walls”?

programme.title: Boxer Rebellion
programme.desc: The Empress Dowager Cixi believes the Boxers’ claim that they have developed a kung fu that makes them impervious to weapons, thus declaring war against the alliances of eight foreign nations. The lack of weapons and good leadership in the Ching government allows the Eight Nation Alliances to take down Beijing.

programme.title: Brothers Five
programme.desc: The five Kao brothers, separated since birth, are unaware that the master of Teng Lung Manor has killed their father. All five however, vow to defeat the vicious gangsters at the manor due to their bullying ways. After reuniting and with much discipline and hard work, the Kaos are prepared to face Lung and his gang.

programme.title: Emperor Chien Lung and the Beauty
programme.desc: Emperor Chien Lung meets a famous courtesan in Suzhou and in order to spend as much time as possible with her, he builds a direct underground tunnel into the Forbidden City. The emperor’s sudden appearances through this direct access shock his people but it is also at this time that he helps the needy and cracks the gambling business in Suzhou.

programme.title: Purple Darts
programme.desc: A girl vows to take revenge for her parents who were murdered by four outlaws when she was only a baby. To do so, she trains hard at martial arts and teams up with a swordsman and a couple to finally kill them all.

programme.title: The Lark
programme.desc: Sixties pop star Carrie Ku plays the "Little Lark" in this romantic-drama of mistaken identity that is a treasure trove of some of the most popular Mandarin songs of all time.

programme.title: Police Force
programme.desc: A man joins the Hong Kong police force to track down a murderer who has killed his friend in a robbery. While he struggles to reconcile his law defending police duty with his desire for vengeance, he also has a new-found respect for the law.

programme.title: The Dream of the Red Chamber
programme.desc: Adapted from the great Chinese classic novel of the same name, the son of renowned Jia family, Bao Yu, is deeply in love with his cousin, Dai Yu. However, his mother disapproves of their relationship and plots to arrange Bao Yu to marry another rich girl, resulting in a tragic ending for the perfect couple.

programme.title: The Reckless Cricket
programme.desc: Inspired by “Drunken Master”, this kung fu comedy features a bumbling martial artist creating a cricket-style fighting arts to fight and defeat the different martial artists who have beaten him before.

programme.title: Asia-pol
programme.desc: Asiapol agent Yang Ming Xuan trails a shipment of contraband gold being delivered to gang leader, George Eaton. He enlists the help of a Chinese woman who is trying to avenge her sister and narrowly escapes several deadly traps as he closes in on Eaton's location. This spy film is loosely inspired by the James Bond movies.

programme.title: Martial Club
programme.desc: The young Wong Fei Hung and his friend Wang Yin Lin find themselves and their martial arts schools pitted against another rival school and the expert they hire, Master Shan. This is a masterpiece of Director Liu Chia Liang and one of the top ten movies in 1981.

programme.title: In The Heart Of The Sea
programme.desc: Oscar® winner Ron Howard (A Beautiful Mind) directs the action adventure based on the best-selling book about the dramatic true journey of the whaling ship Essex. In the winter of 1820, the New England whaling vessel Essex was assaulted by something no one could believe: a whale of mammoth size and will, and an almost human sense of vengeance. The real-life maritime disaster would inspire Herman Melville's Moby Dick. But that told only half the story. In The Heart of The Sea reveals the encounter's harrowing aftermath, as the ship's surviving crew is pushed to their limits and forced to do the unthinkable to stay alive. Braving storms, starvation, panic and despair, the men will call into question their deepest beliefs, from the value of their lives to the morality of their trade, as their captain searches for direction on the open sea and his first mate (The Avengers' Chris Hemsworth) still seeks to bring the great whale down.

Charles is surprisingly supportive of Hawkeye during this troubled time.

programme.title: M*A*S*H S10 Ep22

The I-Corps investigator, Major Van Zandt, determines the goat story implausible and says Hawkeye is responsible and must repay the money. After it is arranged that the goat in question eats Van Zandt’s report, Van Zandt sees things differently and Hawkeye is released from his obligation. While everyone else is concerned with the goat and the payroll, Charles is more concerned with the money he borrowed from Rizzo to buy a vase which turned out to be worthless. Rizzo charges %100 interest per day.

programme.desc: Simon joins an Aussie rancher to round up camels using a specially-adapted off road vehicle and a chopper.

programme.title: Food Factory (S5) Ep9
programme.desc: A single sturgeon can produce a bowl of sustainable caviar worth $12,000; a shepherd's pie puts a modern twist on Mom's classic recipe; a family business rolls out nine million risotto balls every year; and discover the secret to making decadent ice wine truffles.

programme.title: Food Factory (S5) Ep10
programme.desc: See how the cheese met the peanut butter in this legendary sandwich snack; get the scoop on two-toned frozen fruit bars from Florida; 1.5 million blueberry dumplings are produced in just one shift; and it takes a mountain of super-food to make tantalizing kale chips.

programme.title: Animal Einsteins (S1) Ep5
programme.desc: Con Artists - Chris reveals the intelligent cons and deceitful behaviour that Animal Einsteins use to survive and prosper in the game of life - from disguising themselves to outwit predators, and kidnapping babies to save their own offspring, to reading our body language.

programme.title: Great Asian Railway Journeys (S1) Ep2
programme.desc: Chiang Mai to the River Kwai - Michael Portillo embarks on a two-part adventure through Thailand. Michael helps out at an elephant hospital, tries his hand at the art of umbrella-making and learns about northern Thai cuisine.

programme.title: Life Below Zero (S10) Ep14
programme.desc: The Burden of Possessions - With temperatures on the rise, Alaskans must ensure their survival in the hostile Arctic.

programme.title: Extreme Fishing with Robson Green (S4) Ep4
programme.desc: Far East Russia - Robson's Russian adventure starts in the region of Khabarovsk on the quest for one of this area's predators, the Northern Pike.

programme.title: Baby Animals 2 Ep4
programme.desc: Joined at the Hip - The animal kingdom can be a harsh place, but some baby animals have a family ready to take care of their needs. Meet some of these adorable babies and their clans: a koala joey, European elk twins, a litter of Asian short-clawed otters, and black howler monkey youngsters.

programme.title: Arabian Inferno 1 Ep5
programme.desc: Aerial Masters - The Arabian Peninsula is the world’s transit hub for three billion birds on migration to and from Europe, Africa and Asia. This episode tells the stories of the majestic raptors and magnificent waders, from the largest migrants to the smaller residents, and how they fly, hunt and survive in this region of extremes - both in the wild desert and close to the urban jungle.

programme.title: Dawn to Dusk 1 Ep3
programme.desc: A New Zealand Christmas - See how one animal family’s tragedy is another’s holiday dinner as New Zealand’s mainland and island creatures, including penguins, flightless birds, sea lions, and sharks, battle to feed and protect their young in this marine environment.

programme.title: Osprey: Sea Raptor
programme.desc: Osprey: Sea Raptor - A veteran pair of osprey return home to a Connecticut saltmarsh. Over one summer they must battle their enemies, withstand the elements, and hunt hundreds and hundreds of fish, all to raise the next generation of sea raptors.

programme.title: Woodpeckers: The Hole Story 1 Ep1
programme.desc: March to the steady drumbeat of a unique avian family. Learn why the world’s 239 woodpecker species, from massive to minute, are nature’s best lumberjacks; explore their flying, climbing, and calling skills; and get a look inside their secret nests.

programme.title: Rooted 1 Ep2
programme.desc: Sweet Seduction - Discover the story of the much loved Sausage Tree, whose nectar filled blooms and sausage shaped fruits entice animals of all kinds, from insects to elephants. See how the very animals who rely on this generous tree ensure its proliferation.

programme.title: Rooted 1 Ep5
programme.desc: The Hollow Heart - This is the incredible story of a tree that has been around for eight hundred years… that can withstand the harshest conditions… and that is more loved by insects, birds and animals than any other…the enormous Baobab. Rooted on the savannah of Malilangwe Game Reserve in southern Zimbabwe.

programme.title: Baby Animals 2 Ep5
programme.desc: Ugly Cute - Not all baby animals are cute. Often, quirky physical traits are evolutionary adaptations that have helped a species survive. Visit four funny-looking youngsters, including a Baird tapir, two baby gelada baboons, an anteater and a Bactrian camel.

programme.title: Baby Animals 2 Ep6
programme.desc: Primate Families - The sprawling primate family includes animals as different as monkeys, lemurs and humans. Follow primate babies to see how they bond with their mothers, learn to socialize, and adapt to an ever-changing environment.

programme.title: Kenya Wildlife Diaries 1 Ep2
programme.desc: Ivory Wars - Elephant hunting has been banned in Kenya for 40 years. Organized gangs of armed poachers are still targeting elephants, illegally hunting them and selling their ivory tusks on the black market. Environmentalists and conservationists are sounding the alarm.

programme.title: Rewilding 1 Ep1
programme.desc: Return of the European Bison - They are Europe’s biggest terrestrial mammals and the last wild bovine species on the continent. Once the European bison, also known as Wisent, roamed most of the old world, but, unlike its close relative on the other side of the Atlantic, it was hunted to complete extinction by the early 20th century. Only by ambitious rewilding undertakings is it nowadays possible to see these fascinating animals in their natural habitats again.

programme.title: Rewilding 1 Ep2
programme.desc: Hidden Gem of the North - The Steinhuder Meer in the heart of northern Germany is a biodiversity-hotspot in Germany, not far from Hamburg. Different habitats, such as fenlands, alder march, wetlands, and dunes ensure that the largest shallow lake in Germany is extremely attractive to a great variety of different animals, but that's not all: The richly textured landscape is the ideal outdoor laboratory for biologists who operate Germany's significant reintroduction of wildlife.

programme.title: Rewilding 1 Ep3
programme.desc: Andalucia's Struggle - Andalusia is a mosaic of extreme habitats. From the deserted Almeria-region to the snowy mountaintops of the Sierra Nevada, from the dried-out ilex woodlands of the Sierra Morena to the nebulous cork oak forests near Cadiz and Granada’s shrub–covered cliffs. Over the course of histories human settling and hunting had a fundamental impact on these landscapes and their fauna. But today, many of the animals found in Andalusia have found innovative survival strategies and niches that allow them to reclaim Andalusia (only in some cases with a little help of humans).

programme.title: A Wild Year on Earth 1 Ep1
programme.desc: January-February - the Year Begins - In the early months of the year, the Earth’s axial tilt brings the height of summer in some places and the depths of winter in others. See how life struggles to survive under these extreme conditions.

programme.title: A Wild Year on Earth 1 Ep2
programme.desc: March-April - a Time of Renewal - Travel around the globe to witness the atmospheric shifts that take place in March, from the wave of cherry blossoms that unfold across Japan to the final raft of green sea turtles that arrive on the Great Barrier Reef islands to lay eggs.

programme.title: A Wild Year on Earth 1 Ep3
programme.desc: May-June - a Time of Volatility - Watch summer unfold in the Northern Hemisphere, while regions close to the equator enter the wet season and Southern Africa goes dry, creating scarcity for some creatures and bounty for others.

programme.title: New Kids in the Wild 1 Ep1
programme.desc: Lyca the Painted Wolf - In central Namibia, a pack of painted wolves roams the arid land. Amid threats from lions and drought, a plucky little pup called Lyca has to grow up fast, learn the skills of a hunter, and find her place as member of the pack.

programme.title: New Kids in the Wild 1 Ep2
programme.desc: Chinga the Lion Cub - In South Africa’s Greater Kruger Park, A little cub called Chiga has been born into family of hunters - the Mala Mala lion pride. Under the guidance of a devoted father, a fierce mother, and a playful sister, Chiga finds her place in the pride.

programme.title: New Kids in the Wild 1 Ep3
programme.desc: Usana the Cheetah Cub - Usana, a cheetah cub is born with the odds stacked against her. Few cheetah cubs make it through their first year. Lucky for her, she’s got an amazing mother who will stop at nothing to keep her cubs safe. Usana might just follow in her footsteps.

programme.desc: Extreme Sleepover Club / Vega Swift - Smidge, Guy, Cooper, and Biggie throw an impromptu sleepover in the Fun Factory. programme.title: The Mighty Ones Ep11
programme.desc: Two Twigs/Fresh Coat of Pain - The Mighty Ones can't tell the difference between Twig and a random stick bug. / Rocksy sees fresh coat of paint spilled all over and becomes obsessed with trying to freshen up the yard.

programme.title: The Adventures Of Puss In Boots Ep41
programme.desc: In Dreams - When Puss asks the second witch sister Malaranea for her gem, she casts a spell that makes him a prisoner in his dreams and only Dulcinea can save him

programme.title: Noddy Toyland Detective Ep5
programme.desc: The Case Of The Lost Space Rocket - Smartysaurus is going to launch into space in her all-new super space rocket. But as her friends all watch on the Daredale Big Screen, the picture suddenly goes dead! Noddy investigates to find out what happened to Smartysaurus.

programme.title: Noddy Toyland Detective Ep6
programme.desc: The Case Of The Smartysaurus's Jet Pack - Smartysaurus is trying out her new jet pack, but she hasn't read the instructions before taking off and cannot control it properly. Noddy investigates to help her control it before things get too dangerous.

programme.title: Noddy Toyland Detective Ep7
programme.desc: The Case Of The Topsy Turvy Trees - All is set for the Toy Green Picnic until Noddy finds some of the trees turned upside down! Was it the Ninjas climbing on them? Or the Pirates wanting an upside-down tree for Pirate Bay? Noddy launches an investigation to find out who's behind all this.

programme.title: Noddy Toyland Detective Ep8
programme.desc: The Case Of The Golden Thing - The Knights have found a mysterious Golden Thing. But the Pirates insist it's their Golden Thing. Noddy tries to settle the argument by investigating: Who is the owner of the Golden Thing? He soon finds more and more Golden Things have been hidden all over Toyland.

programme.title: Raa Raa The Noisy Lion Ep5
programme.desc: Zebby's Snack Time - Zebby likes to have a snack when she is feeling tired. Raa Raa thinks this is a great idea and decides to join his friend. Except he thinks they should have their snack in the perfect place… but everywhere they try is just too noisy… I wonder why that could be?!

programme.title: Raa Raa The Noisy Lion Ep6
programme.desc: Finding Noisy - Raa Raa gets carried away when collecting fun noisy objects in the jungle with his friends. Raa Raa wants to keep everything he finds for himself, but soon discovers that his collection isn't much fun with nobody to share it with.

programme.title: Raa Raa The Noisy Lion Ep7
programme.desc: Ooo Ooo's Jungle Drums - Raa Raa has found an infectious beat, and soon all the other animals in the jungle are joining in… except for Ooo Ooo, who just can't get the beat right. How can they find a way for all the friends to play together?

programme.title: Raa Raa The Noisy Lion Ep8
programme.desc: Topsy's Musical Stones - Topsy has readied the musical stones for a noisy game. Raa Raa has been left in charge, making sure that nobody jumps on them while Topsy reminds the other jungle inhabitants about the game. But temptation can be strong… especially when Ooo Ooo is about...

programme.title: Roary The Racing Car Ep5
programme.desc: Car Boot Sale - Big Chris has a clear out and takes all his old junk up to Farmer Green's car boot sale but misses the clutter in Rusty. How will he get everything back?

programme.title: Roary The Racing Car Ep6
programme.desc: Hot Stuff - Big Chris takes the cars to the beach to relax in the heat but he is so busy dealing with the cars he forgets to drink his water. But hang on, who else has drunk it…

programme.title: Roary The Racing Car Ep7
programme.desc: Law And Order - Mr Carburettor is fed up with the cars running amok on his track and summons Bill and Nick to restore order to the track. But might our overzealous policeman overstep the mark?

programme.title: Roary The Racing Car Ep8
programme.desc: Flash's Tea Party - Flash invites everyone to a tea party, thinking they bring the food with them. Are there going to be a lot of hungry bunnies at Silver hatch?

programme.title: Casper's Scare School Ep3
programme.desc: Bully For You / The Ra Animator - Bully For You When Casper decides he can't take any more of Thatch's nastiness, he forms a secret squad dedicated to putting an end to bullying. The Ra-minator Using the power of invisibility, Casper offers to help transform Ra from a sports zero to an athletic hero.

programme.title: Casper's Scare School Ep4
programme.desc: Weekend At Bunny's / Grimly Day - Weekend at Bunny's Alder and Dash sound the alarm after a terrifying creature threatens Scare School. Grimly Day It's Grimly Day?the grimmest day of the year!

programme.title: Where's Wally? Ep12
programme.desc: Venice the Menace - The Wanderers head to Venice to get a new cookie jar from Venice. Odlulu aims to become belle of the ball at the Venice Carnival but when she gets hold of the Crystal Glass Key, she turns the canals of Venice to glass. The Wanderers must get the key back and restore the city to normal.

programme.title: Archibald's Next Big Thing Is Here! Ep38
programme.desc: A Star Is Hatched / Say Cheese - After stumbling into Finly’s music performance, Archibald’s unique sound leads to a hit record. But as the pressures of fame and success loom over the band, they struggle to recreate that "Archibald sound" and recapture lightning in a bottle. / When the Strutters need a family portrait, they meet a burnt out photographer named Randy. After accidentally wrecking his studio, Archibald decides he’s going to help Randy rekindle his passion for photography.

programme.title: Boss Baby: Back in Business Ep23
programme.desc: Picture Perfect - Tim and Boss Baby want to bond with Dad by recreating a perfect "Dudes Weekend' camping trip, culminating in a photo opp, but everything seems to go wrong

programme.title: Boss Baby: Back in Business Ep24
programme.desc: Play It Again, Tim - When Tim is forced to take piano lessons, he actually enjoys them and Boss Baby realizes that Tim is being brainwashed by his piano teacher, slowly turning Tim into an old man

programme.title: The Epic Tales of Captain Underpants Ep18
programme.desc: Captain Underpants and the Dastardlys Deed of the Devious Diddlysaurus - George and Harold decide to do an extra credit project on dinosaurs to help their chances of getting summer camp-worthy grades. When Melvin brings in a dinosaur frozen in ice, the boys try to get rid of it. But the ice thaws and they meet Diddlysaurus, a prankster raptor who's huge fans of the boys. He offers to help them with their project if he can pull pranks with them, but when the pranks go too far, the boys and Captain Underpants have to deal with the dino.

programme.title: The Epic Tales of Captain Underpants Ep19
programme.desc: Captain Underpants and the Shadowy Syndrome of the Sinister Splotch - Captain Underpants becomes a wanted man in underwear when footage surfaces of a robber who looks exactly like him. George and Harold, positive it's an impostor, try to track down the perp and bring him to justice. But can the boys do this before Captain Underpants is found guilty?

programme.title: The Epic Tales of Captain Underpants Ep25
programme.desc: Captain Underpants and the Taxing Trauma of the Treacherous Tattle Trials Part I - In part one of a two-part season finale, the Melvins create a final exam that George and Harold will be sure to fail: the Doom Dome. To ensure success, Melvinborg injects Melvin's cells with nanobots, giving him heightened powers. But when George and Harold find out, they crank the nanobots to the max, causing Melvin to grow into a giant! The boys enlist Captain Underpants to fight the jealous nerd, but their victory only loses the nanobots onto Piqua...

programme.title: The Epic Tales of Captain Underpants Ep26
programme.desc: Captain Underpants and the Taxing Trauma of the Treacherous Tattle Trials Part II - Part two of the season finale finds George, Harold, Captain Underpants, and the Melvins trapped in the Doom Dome with rampaging nanobots. When the humans try to neautralize the bots, they find a new host: Captain Underpants. Now they must shrink down to go into Captain Underpants’ brain and defeat the nanobots’ leader, Nanozero. But they need help: Captain Underpants’ brain cells to the rescue! And when it’s all over, George and Harold will finally be able to go to summer camp.

programme.title: Trollhunters: Tales of Arcadia Ep24
programme.desc: Angor Management - Jim and Strickler team up to bring down Angor Rot Meanwhile the Gnome returns with important information regarding Baby Enrique.

programme.title: Kung Fu Panda: The Paws Of Destiny Ep23
programme.desc: Bridge Over Troubled Lava - The whole gang escapes pursing Guards, battles flowing lava, and survives crumbling caves and pillars to finally make it back to the Forbidden City. Xiao is ready to escape the palace, but Shi Long has other plans for her.

programme.title: Kung Fu Panda: The Paws Of Destiny Ep24
programme.desc: House of Flying Pandas - The gang learns of even bigger and direr forces working against the Empress and the Kingdom of China, and must come up with a plan to put a stop to it before it is too late.

programme.title: Dragons: Race to the Edge Ep12
programme.desc: The Next Big Sting - Hiccup, Toothless and the Dragon Riders rescue a wounded Speed Stinger and take it back to Dragon's Edge, unaware of the dangers that follow.

programme.title: The Mighty Ones Ep12
programme.desc: A Stinky Situation /Fire-Fly - When Twig gets sprayed by a skunk trying to save his friends, the Mighty Ones agree not to ruin his hero moment by telling him that the stinks. Instead, they try to wash the smell off of him without him knowing. / The Mighty Ones are cold so when they hear about a wonderful creature known as a "fire-fly," they decide it will be the answer to their problems.

programme.title: All Hail King Julien Ep23
programme.desc: The King Who Would Be King - Fred the Giant Scorpion vows revenge after he reads an untrue story about himself in King Julien's new book.

programme.title: All Hail King Julien Ep24
programme.desc: Are You There Frank? It's Me, King Julien - Frank the Sky God comes to the lemur kingdom to prove his existence – and to demand the ultimate sacrifice: King Julien himself.

programme.title: Cleopatra In Space Ep25
